#registration
  %section#faq
    %h2 Course Information
    .border-line
    .questions
      .question
        What is LevelUp Build?
      .answer
        LevelUp Build is an
        %u 8 week
        program designed to bridge the gap between university and your first full time job.

      .question
        Audience
      .answer
        LevelUp is for people who are seeking industry experience such as:
        %ul#selector
          %li students approaching the end of their course
          %li people who are self taught
          %li people who are changing career
        This program is aimed at anyone interested in development, business analysts and experience design in agile teams.

      .question
        Prerequisites
      .answer
        Some skills that are required for specific roles are:
        %ul#selector
          %li Developers: You must be able to program in one language. If you've never done any programming before you should check out the other roles.
          %li Business Analysts: Good analytical and communication skills
          %li Experience designers: A background in visual or interface design

      .question
        Computer Requirements
      .answer
        All developers
        %u are expected to bring a laptop
        and have their machine configured before attending LevelUp.
        %a{href:""} [Preparing your laptop for LevelUp Build]
        %br
        For other roles, a laptop is not essential but would be good to have. It is important to note that other people will be using your laptop with you, however, not without supervision.

      .question
        Topics
      .answer
        %ul#selector
          %li Agile software development
          %li Test Driven Development (TDD)
          %li Pairing
          %li Continuous integration (CI)
          %li Story writing
          %li Social contract
          %li Collaborative sketching
          %li Working in cross functional teams
          %li Retrospectives
          %li Test automation
          %li Continuous delivery
          %li Inceptions

      .question
        Price
      .answer
        %u FREE!
        LevelUp is free for participants.

      .question
        Where
      .answer
        ThoughtWorks Sydney, Level 8, 51 Pitt Street, Sydney NSW 2000

      .question
        When
      .answer
        %ul#selector
        %li Kickoff day: 11th of April, 10am - 5pm
        %li Sessions: Start 14th of April, every Tuesday night from 6pm till 9pm, for 8 weeks.

      .question
        Am I guaranteed a spot if I register?
      .answer
        To make this the best experience we can, we need cross functional teams with the right combination of people in each role (developer, business analyst and tester). Whilst the LevelUp team would love to accept everyone, places are limited.

      .question
        For more information please contact us at:
        %a{:href => "mailto:levelup@thoughtworks.com"} levelup@thoughtworks.com
        or check our FAQ page.


